Master

Class Master.Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • Master.Master.Task
  • Enclosing class:
    Master

    private class Master.Task
extends java.lang.Object
    The Task class is used for master to keep track of what is necessary to process a request. Master creates a Task when receiving a message from a client or CS Master queues Tasks and uses this class to call actions
